9b    ; 9b - Unknown code of aircraft
9b-1  ; 9b - Missing code of aircraft
9c-1  ; 9c - Unkwnown value of wake turbulence cat
9c-2  ; 9c - Other value of wake turbulence cat

10a-1 ; 10a - Unknown equipment COM,NAV
10a-2 ; 10a - Equipment "N" means no equipment on board
10a-3 ; 10a - Unalowed equipment code or codes combination
10b-1 ; 10b - Missing describtion of equipment SSR
10b-2 ; 10b - Uncorrect length of equipment SSR array
10b-3 ; 10b - Uncorrect equipment SSR

13a   ; 13  - Array is not written according to ICAO rules
13a-1 ; 13a - Departure aerodrome is not written according to ICAO rules
13a-2 ; 13a - Invalid or missing value/format of estimated departure time
13a-3 ; 13a - Missing departure aerodrome code
13b-1 ; 13b - Invalid or missing value/format of real departure time

14a   ; 14a - Unknown input/crossing point
14b   ; 14b - Invalid or missing value of estimated time
14c   ; 14c - Invalid or missing value of flight level
14d   ; 14d - Invalid or missing value of first flight level
14e   ; 14e - "A"scending or "B"ellow enabled

15a   ; 15a - Invalid or missing value/format of cruising speed (i.e. K0900,N400,M0910)
15a-1 ; 15a - Speed is to low
15a-2 ; 15a - Speed is to high

15b   ; 15b - Invalid or missing  value/format of flight level (i.e. F340,S1120,A045,M0900)
15b-1 ; 15b - Altitude is to low
15b-2 ; 15b - Altitude is to high

15c-2 ; 15c - Point expected (i.e. C/POINT/K0650F340F360)
15c-3 ; 15c - Speed expected (i.e. C/POINT/K0650F340F360)
15c-4 ; 15c - Flight level value expected (i.e. C/POINT/K0650F340F360)
15c-7 ; 15c - Expected cruise climb (K0760S0965)
15c-8 ; 15c - Invalid or missing value/format of speed (i.e. K0900,N400,M0910)
15c-9 ; 15c - Invalid or missing value/format of flight level (i.e. F340,S1120,A045,M0900)

15c-10; 15c - Unknown code of point or route                             ; pri dekodovani neznamy bod medzi znamymi
15c-11; 15c - Unable to decode known points or routes
15c-12; 15c - There are no points on the route
15c-15; 15c - Stopover is not enabled

15c-25; 15c - There is not specified intersection points of routes
15c-26; 15c - There more possible intersection points of routes
15c-27; 15c - There is not intersection points of routes
15c-28; 15c - The point not belong to the route, their distance is to large
15c-29; 15c - The point not belong  of the route
15c-30; 15c - Point does'nt belong on the route
15c-31; 15c - Points does'nt belong to the same route, "DCT" is expected
15c-32; 15c - Points are to be separated by "DCT"

15c-36; 15c - Departure aerodrome is to far from first point of the route
15c-37; 15c - Destination aerodrome is to far from route
15c-38; 15c - Cannot determine input point on route
15c-39; 15c - Cannot determine output point on route
15c-40; 15c - Decoded route does'nt begin on aerodrome in or input into controlled area
15c-41; 15c - Decoded route does'nt end on aerodrome in or output from controlled area
15c-42; 15c - Internal flight with unknown points on the route
15c-50; 15c - Cannot determine input or output point of the route

16a   ; 16 - Array is not written according to ICAO rules
16a-1 ; 16a - Destination aerodrome is not written according to ICAO rules
16a-2 ; 16a - Invalid or missing value/format  of flight time
16a-3 ; 13a - Missing arrival aerodrome code
16b-1 ; 16b - Backup aerodromes are not written according to ICAO rules

18    ; 18 - Other information
18-1  ; 18 - Another keyword
18-2  ; 18 - Expected
18-3  ; 18 - is expected by 18 ("ZZZZ" is used)
18-4  ;

18-10 ; 18 - Departure aerodrome is not in FIR, there is expected EET/
18-11 ; 18 - Invalid or missing format/time value of EET

18-20 ; 18 - Invalid or missing date of flight
18-21 ; 18 - Not actual date of flight

18-50 ; Date of flight requested in format rrmmdd, i.e. 970531
18-51 ; Last date of flight is before first one
18-52 ; There is no flight planned during the week

19-1  ; Empty array 19 ("SUPLEMENTARY INFORMATION")
20-1  ; Empty array 20 ("ALERTING SEARCH AND RESCUE INFORMATION")
21-1  ; Empty array 21 ("RADIO FAILURE INFORMATION")

22-1  ; Error in array 22


